{"type": "article", "id": 29563, "title": "飞碟形的极简灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-13T23:08:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607131636124v8Q32YdPslSDJmi.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>灯具品牌 <a href=\"http://nemolighting.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nemo</a> 最新推出 Olympia 是一个极简而抽象的灯具系列，由 <a href=\"http://www.fuksas.com/en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fuksas</a> 工作室的 Doriana 和 Massimiliano Fuksas 共同设计完成。黑白相间的柔光罩借鉴了飞碟的造型，亮灯后会让光线产生 360 度的发散，看上去就好像悬浮在空中一样，透露出一股神秘的气息。灯罩通过活动长臂与底座相连，可以根据需要自由调节，适用于各种不同的环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607131636345ZKPMnJF2hbOaeSE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.436430\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713163634qwA2IFrZkYp7zVtn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713163634SuNE7CHegdMBqsXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.916870\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160713163634LpMO5kbxsjn9JlwK.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.970660\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}